quite the coincidence, mo!

rows.label: tlk000601_01_msg0002

The inn I always patronize
is called Jakolo's, mo.

rows.label: tlk000601_01_msg0003

springs are so pleasant, it's a wonderful place, mo~!

rows.label: tlk000601_01_msg0004

I'll tell them to give you a cheap room,
so please be sure to stop by, mo.
